name: nursing-homes-minnesota-2003
notes: The nursing home facilities are from the Minnesota Department of Health state registration and licensure Health Care Facility and Provider Database. http://www.health.state.mn.us/divs/fpc/directory/fpcdir.html This database offers addresses, phone numbers, administrator names and state registration or licensure status for Minnesota health care providers. Federal certification classifications are also included.
